---
import Base from '../../layouts/Base.astro';
---

<Base title="Insights — needle-bench" description="Data-driven analysis of AI coding agents. Model comparisons, open vs closed source benchmarks, and debugging performance across 26 models and 1,664 runs.">
  <div class="page-header">
    <div class="page-header-left">
      <a href="/" class="back">&larr; Leaderboard</a>
      <h1>Insights</h1>
    </div>
    <nav class="page-header-right">
      <a href="https://github.com/os-tack/find-the-needle">GitHub</a>
      <a href="/about/">About</a>
    </nav>
  </div>

  <main>
    <section class="section">
      <p>Analysis from 26 models &times; 32 benchmarks &times; 2 experimental arms = 1,664 runs. Every claim cites specific data. No marketing.</p>
    </section>

    <section class="section">
      <h2>Articles</h2>
      <div class="insight-list">
        <a href="/insights/model-comparison/" class="insight-card">
          <h3>AI Coding Model Comparison: 26 Models on Real Bugs</h3>
          <p class="muted">Head-to-head benchmark results. Claude, GPT, Gemini, DeepSeek, Grok, Mistral, Llama, Qwen — tested on identical bugs with deterministic scoring.</p>
        </a>
        <a href="/insights/open-vs-closed/" class="insight-card">
          <h3>Open vs Closed Source Models for Debugging</h3>
          <p class="muted">DeepSeek, Devstral, Llama, and Qwen vs Claude, GPT, and Gemini. The gap is smaller than you think — and context injection changes the math.</p>
        </a>
      </div>
    </section>
  </main>
</Base>

<style>
  .insight-list {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 1rem;
  }

  .insight-card {
    display: block;
    padding: 1.25rem 1.5rem;
    background: var(--surface);
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    border-radius: 6px;
    color: var(--text);
    transition: border-color 0.15s;
  }

  .insight-card:hover {
    border-color: var(--accent);
    color: var(--text);
  }

  .insight-card h3 {
    font-family: var(--mono);
    font-size: 1rem;
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
    color: var(--accent);
  }

  .insight-card .muted {
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    color: var(--text-muted);
    line-height: 1.5;
  }
</style>
